    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved by its sole owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-new condition, with the leather upholstery still firm and smelling fresh, and every electronic component functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at the dealership according to a strict schedule. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "mint",
