    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it's been garaged since day one and honestly still looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like an absolute dream and I've pampered it with regular detailing and on-time servicing. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions or if you want to come take a peek. You won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44000.0,
