    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E39 M5 is a definitive example of the analog sports sedan. The S62 4.9L V8 engine maintains factory-spec compression and exhibits flawless double-VANOS timing. Power is channeled through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a 25% locking limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and linear torque delivery. The chassis features a lightweight aluminum multi-link suspension with zero play in the bushings, ensuring the communicative steering remains razor-sharp. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this vehicle retains its original aerodynamic underbody cladding and factory-spec heat shielding. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning driver.",
